Original summary was: Log Configuration UI does NOT validate the "File Appender Pattern"

I don't see why we let people change this,  If someone really wants to change it, they can edit the config.
But if we are going to keep it, we should have some sort of validation on the field

The pattern we use: %4d{yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss} %-5p [%-15.15t] - %c - %m%n

A pattern of: !@#$%^&*()_+
